{"tid":559114,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"女大生一夜情後提告　「男友來電」竟救了那位砲友","createTime":"2018-02-13T01:59:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-13T03:17:07.000Z","uid":122,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2bb899bb1952a71c7030ec074898e3f5bab02c53","tid":559114,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T01:59:22.000Z","msg":"《聯合報》報導，北部一名陳姓男大生（18歲）去年用通訊軟體搭訕正妹女大生，兩人相談甚歡，隨後約旅館開房間發生性行為。<br />\n <br />\n不料女大生事後提告，指陳男在房內強行壓制、性侵得逞，讓她身心受創。<br />\n <br />\n男大生喊冤，稱兩人見面後感覺不錯，自然而然發生性行為，他認為是「一夜情」；期間因房間停電，旅館員工進房維修，女生未呼救、也無異狀。<br />\n <br />\n過程中，女大生還接到男友打來的電話，對方問她在哪，女大生表示跟朋友在一起，聊了3、4分鐘，也沒有求救。<br />\n <br />\n檢方調閱監視器畫面，確認兩人手牽手進旅館、手牽手離開，認定全案僅女大生單一指述，陳姓男大生罪嫌不足，處分不起訴。（王嘉慶／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://assets.sbnation.com/assets/2860709/luizdenies.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fassets.sbnation.com%2Fassets%2F2860709%2Fluizdenies.gif&h=cf82c9d9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"89309c46b0c8f257606e0f519389bb71888aa8c5","tid":559114,"uid":140736,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T02:00:50.000Z","msg":"#metoo"},{"pid":"f910f6d8c4a1b1b8efc41ddd8e04cde9370021aa","tid":559114,"uid":73092,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T02:07:54.000Z","msg":"救空門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2e90bd99279102cf1d039e55322a420f15dbecb","tid":559114,"uid":68094,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T02:09:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7510e1ccdfebeef92cc1b476f9a655094759aed6","tid":559114,"uid":23887,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T02:09:15.000Z","msg":"張gif用lord賓幫猁救空門會貼切d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50e1177296c0133be61a539249370b766f6dc299","tid":559114,"uid":21028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f2e90bd99279102cf1d039e55322a420f15dbecb","tid":559114,"uid":68094,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"cite